  "texts": [
    "We also excluded models that were ensembles of other models in our pool.",
    "This led to a set of 9 individual models.",
    "In building ensemble models, an equally weighted mean at each quantile level was employed.",
    "In Massachusetts in 2021, the importance metrics of component models were correlated with model accuracy as measured by -WIS.",
    "Specifically, the more accurate a model's predictions were on average (as the value of negative WIS increases, it indicates higher accuracy), the higher the importance that model had (larger values indicate more important forecasts)(Figure 4)."
